<org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmlns:epf="http://www.eclipse.org/epf" epf:version="1.5.1" xmlns:rmc="http://www.ibm.com/rmc" rmc:version="7.5.1" xmi:id="-UA3Wb-AnbujrELbLKi2YHQ" name="secure_sponsor,_2Yh4gPHCEdqvbZNHa620Yw" guid="-UA3Wb-AnbujrELbLKi2YHQ" changeDate="2007-05-08T16:21:30.859-0700" version="1.0.0">
  <mainDescription>&lt;p>&#xD;
    The Reuse Strategy, Reuse Assessment, and Asset Financial Estimate should be reviewed by the Sponsor. The Sponsor is&#xD;
    impacted by the work of the proposed asset activities and sees value in funding the asset program.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The Sponsor needs to determine the commitment level for funding, whether it is a short term funding or a long term, or&#xD;
    with key milestones and progress reports.&#xD;
&lt;/p>&#xD;
&lt;p>&#xD;
    The funding models should be discussed with the Sponsor and the needs of the Sponsor should be addressed.. When&#xD;
    necessary refinements to the reuse strategy should be made to meet the needs of the Sponsor..&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
  <sections xmi:id="_-4xscP26Edubna2vE0o6gQ" name="Review the Estimates with the Sponsor" guid="_-4xscP26Edubna2vE0o6gQ">
    <sectionDescription>The financial estimates should be reviewed with the Sponsor.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_BE17YP27Edubna2vE0o6gQ" name="Understand Sponsor Needs" guid="_BE17YP27Edubna2vE0o6gQ">
    <sectionDescription>The needs of the Sponsor need to be balanced with the intended reuse scope. If the expected reuse scope is not in line with&#xD;
the Sponsor then this needs to be addressed or the asset program will suffer from conflicting goals.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <sections xmi:id="_CkqIUP27Edubna2vE0o6gQ" name="Refine the Strategy" guid="_CkqIUP27Edubna2vE0o6gQ">
    <sectionDescription>Update the Reuse Strategy as necessary to meet the needs of the Sponsor.</sectionDescription>
  </sections>
  <purpose>&lt;p>&#xD;
    Establish a committed financial provider.&#xD;
&lt;/p></purpose>
</org.eclipse.epf.uma:TaskDescription>
